data.text:
TFRRS

Outdoor 2020: Placed eighth in the long jump in his only competition of the outdoor season at the Beach Opener.

Indoor 2019-20: Opened his junior campaign with a victory in the triple jump and a third place finish in the long jump at the Crowell Open...finished third in the long jump at the Army Open...recorded a second place finish in the triple jump at the Nittany Lion Challenge...placed eighth in the long jump at the Keydet Invitational...placed second in the triple jump and fourth in the long jump at the Army-Navy Star Meet...won the long jump at the Army Open...finished fifth in the triple jump and sixth in the long jump at the Patriot League Championships.

Outdoor 2019: Started the outdoor campaign with a 13th place finish in the long jump at the Ben Brown Invitational..placed second in the triple jump and fifth in the long jump at the UC Irvine Spring Break Classic...won the triple jump at the Army-Navy Star Meet...posted a personal best 6.86m in the long jump and a fourth place finish in the triple jump at the Patriot League Championships.

Indoor 2018-19: Opened the season with a victory in the triple jump at the Crowell Open...finished third in the triple jump at the Nittany Lion Challenge...placed second with a personal best 14.82m mark in the triple jump at the Army-Navy Star Meet...posted a fifth place finish in the triple jump at the Patriot League Championships.

Outdoor 2018: Started the season with a win at the Ben Brown Invitational in the triple jump... Placed seventh in the long jump and fourth in the triple jump at the UC Irvine Spring Break Classic... At the Penn Challenge, won the triple jump and finished seventh in the long jump... Was the triple jump runner-up at the Army Navy Outdoor Star Meet... Took third in the same event at the Larry Ellis Invitational... Ended the season in seventh in the triple jump at the Patriot League Championships.

Indoor 2017-18: Started the season at the Crowell Open with a pair of third place finishes in the long jump and triple jump... At the Leonard Hilton Invitational placed fifth in the triple jump... Took seventh in the triple jump at the Penn 8-Team Select... At the Penn State National Invitational, finished fifth int he triple jump... Was the runner-up in the triple jump at the Army Navy Indoor Star Meet...Ended the season with a third place finish in the triple jump at the Patriot League Championships.

Background: Bender comes to West Point from Fairfax High School…named Athlete of the Year…earned Scholar Athlete honors… majoring in Engineering Management with a minor in Biology.
